des:
Invocation Name: my dishwasher
Using this skill, you can ask status of Midea dishwasher or cancel/pause Midea dishwasher.
After the user wakes up the speaker by “Alexa, my dishwasher.” to call this skill, you can easily interactive with the dishwasher.
Uses must do Account Linking following the steps below:
1. Click the ENABLE button, then enter the registered MSmartLife app account.
2. If you do not have a MSmartLife, please download MSmartLife App from Apple AppStore or Google Play
3. After installation and registration, complete the dishwasher activation configuration.
4. Back to the Account Linking interface of Alexa APP, enter the registered MSmartLife App account to complete Account Linking.
